# Closeout

Triggers: `close out thread`, `closeout`, `end thread`, `wrap this chat`

Run `context_window_closeout.cmd --record` (auto-ship per `auto-ship.mdc`).

Charter/explore mixed-plane → park only, no branch surgery.

End with one line: "Thread closed — work shipped" or "Thread closed — parked."

